org.ftcbootstrap.demos.navbot

Class NavBot

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ftcbootstrap.RobotConfiguration
      • org.ftcbootstrap.demos.navbot.NavBot

  • public class NavBot
extends RobotConfiguration
    PushBot Saved Configuration

    It is assumed that there is a configuration on the phone running the Robot Controller App with the same name as this class and that configuration is the one that is marked 'activated' on the phone.

    It is also assumed that the device names in the 'init()' method below are the same as the devices named for the saved configuration on the phone.
